<TABLE ALIGN=MIDDLE WIDTH=80%>
<TR>
<TD>
<b>Bayesian Data Analysis:</b> The third edition of Bayesian Data Analysis by A. Gelman,
J. B. Carlin, H. S. Stern, and D. B. Rubin was published in 2014.  The new edition
includes additional chapters on computation and Bayesian nonparametric modeling tools. It also includes illustrations of computation using STAN.
For additional information about this book including how to purchase
please visit the <A HREF="http://www.stat.columbia.edu/~gelman/book">book web site</A>.
