<b><i>CHANCE</i> magazine:</b> <i>Chance</i> is a magazine about statistics
and the use of statistics in society.  <i>Chance</i> features
articles that showcase the use of
statistical methods and ideas in the social,
biological, physical, and medical
sciences. I'm a former editor and a big fan!
Please visit the <A HREF="http://chance.amstat.org">web site</A> for more information. </td>
